processDocumentation.geographyDescription: This process assumes an average emissions rate based on a route from XX to YY. The route is also used to estimate the portion of emissions that occur within an Emissions Control Area (ECA), where reduced emissions are required.  Note no location object is assigned as emissions are primarily occuring in  open waters.
